claims the companys lewis property covers an area of about  acres contiguous with phoenix gold mine placed into production by newmont mining its property hosts a series of gold mines including marigold fortitude lone tree phoenix midas twin creeks and trenton canyon bmg is headquartered in vancouver british columbia canada table of contents  battle mountain gold inc  business analysis      battle mountain gold inc  company overview      battle mountain gold inc  major products and services  battle mountain gold inc  analysis of key performance indicators      battle mountain gold inc  five year snapshot overview of financial and operational performance indicators      battle mountain gold inc  key financial performance indicators        battle mountain gold inc  solvency      battle mountain gold inc  key competitors  battle mountain gold inc  recent developments  battle mountain gold inc  key employees  appendix      methodology      ratio definitions      disclaimer list of tables table  battle mountain gold inc  major products and services table  battle mountain gold inc  key ratios  annual table  battle mountain gold inc  key ratios  interim table  battle mountain gold inc  key capital market indicators table  battle mountain gold inc  key employees list of figures figure  battle mountain gold inc  solvency request a sample report name email optional request you to please fill in your corporate emailid job title company phone no your country select country afghanistan albania algeria american samoa andorra angola anguilla antigua  barbuda argentina armenia aruba australia austria azerbaijan bahamas bahrain bangladesh barbados belarus belgium belize benin bermuda bhutan bolivia bosnia  herzegovina botswana brazil brunei bulgaria burkina faso burundi cambodja cameroon canada cape verde cayman islands central african republic chad chile china colombia comoros congobrazzaville congokinshasa cook islands costa rica cote divoire croatia cuba cyprus czech republic denm