ries bmg operates and owns  and has an option to earn the remaining  of the flagship lewis project situated in the prolific battle mountain trend of nevada the acre lewis property is contiguous with the  million ounce phoenix gold mine placed into production by newmont mining in late  please refer to corporate presentation dated february   also please refer to corporate presentation dated july   and abridged corporate presentation dated august   for full description and results images and photos of bmg – newmont boundary area the technical information in this website about activities on the lewis project from june   onwards has been prepared by the company’s qualified person steven garwin phd a director of the company a fellow of the australian institute of geoscientists and a fellow of the australasian institute of mining and metallurgy the technical information in this website on activities on the lewis project prior to june  is based upon a report under national instrument filed on sedar march   and titled amended and restated summary report  core and reverse circulation drilling program fw lewis property battle mountain mining district lander county nevada usa the “  report” dr garwin has reviewed the   report and has approved the written disclosure drawn therefrom set out in this website join our email list your name email country country afghanistan albania algeria american samoa andorra angola anguilla antigua  barbuda argentina armenia aruba australia austria azerbaijan azores bahamas bahrain bangladesh barbados belarus belgium belize benin bermuda bhutan bolivia bonaire bosnia  herzegovina botswana brazil british indian ocean ter brunei bulgaria burkina faso burundi cambodia cameroon canada canary islands cape verde cayman islands central african republic chad channel islands chile china christmas island cocos island columbia comoros congo cook islands costa rica cote divoire croatia cuba curacao cyprus czech republic denmark djibouti dominica dominican rep